Amanda Abbington https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amanda_Abbington 0 Amanda Abbington (born Amanda Jane Smith; 28 February 1974) is an English actress. She is best known for playing Miss Mardle in Mr Selfridge and Mary Morstan in the BBC adaptation of Sherlock. Amanda_Abbington ( born Amanda_Jane_Smith ; 28_February_1974 ) is an_English_actress .
